---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 rounded-md bg-accent"></span><span class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Exclusive Mentorship</span></div>
      <p>&copy; {year} · All rights reserved</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <a href="/refund" class="hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors">Refund</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      <span class="font-semibold text-gray-500">Risk disclaimer:</span> Trading financial markets involves substantial risk and is not suitable for everyone. This mentorship is for educational purposes only and is not financial advice. Past performance does not guarantee future results. You may lose some or all of your capital. Never trade with money you cannot afford to lose.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
